I feel like while Jirou would be fine with announcing the relationship, Tsuyu would be...
body:
For @bnha-rarepair-months Secrets prompt

I feel like while Jirou would be fine with announcing the relationship, Tsuyu would be scared of possible backlash and wouldn’t be sure what her family’s reaction would be. She wants to tell her friends, but for the time being they keep everything behind closed doors.

blog.name: quirk-emporium
blog.title: Horikoshi Please Hire Me
blog.description: Hi! I’m Mod Tokoyami and I write quirks, welcome to my quirk concept blog! Feel free to submit any ideas/questions you have for oc quirks and I’ll write them down! Thanks!

body:
Welcome Welcome

I’m Mod Tokoyami and welcome to my quirk concept blog! In this blog I will answer for the following -

- quirk ideas following a theme (for example, ice quirks)

- quirk marriage ideas (no quirk marriage ideas for pedophilia/incest ships I swear to god please do not)

- quirk drawbacks for any existing oc quirks

- questions on whether or not a quirk is op

- how would certain characters fare against your character’s quirk

- I’m prettt sure this isn’t all of it but it will be updated if needed

Thank you and welcome to heck!
